<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{notificationTitle}} - IECA</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7c3aed 0%, #5b21b6 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .logo {
            max-width: 120px;
            height: auto;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        .notification-box {
            background: #f3f4f6;
            border-left: 4px solid #7c3aed;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6 0%, #1d4ed8 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .footer {
            background: #f1f5f9;
            padding: 20px 30px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #64748b;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <img src="cid:ieca-logo" alt="IECA Logo" class="logo">
            <h1>ðŸ”” IECA Notification</h1>
            <p>Indian Error Cyber Army</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear <strong>{{name}}</strong>,</p>
            
            <p>
                You have received a new notification from the Indian Error Cyber Army platform.
            </p>
            
            <div class="notification-box">
                <h3>{{notificationTitle}}</h3>
                <p>{{notificationMessage}}</p>
            </div>
            
            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="{{websiteUrl}}/portal/notifications" class="cta-button">
                    View All Notifications ðŸ“‹
                </a>
            </div>
            
            <p>
                You can manage your notification preferences in your account settings to control which types of notifications you receive via email.
            </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>
                <strong>Indian Error Cyber Army (IECA)</strong><br>
                Notification System
            </p>
            <p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12px;">
                To unsubscribe from notifications, visit your account settings or contact support.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
